Second, I&#39;ll assume you take the approach of writing tests in Kotlin, but still using those functions in Java code. Otherwise, if your codebase is in Kotlin only, this test is pointless.

Third, if you try to assign `null` to `@NotNull` parameter, you should receive `IllegalArgumentException`, not `InvalidParameterException`

